---
title: Crispy Skinned Duck and Cherry Sauce with Chive Mash and Broccolini
description: It's time to elevate your winter dinner with juicy crispy duck breast, tender broccolini and a savoury-sweet cherry sauce. You won't believe how easy this 5-star meal comes together, you'll impress yourself and any guest!
